  <description>
    <p>Hosty helps you create, run, and manage local Fabric Minecraft servers with a native GNOME interface.</p>
    <p>Use Hosty to create servers, monitor performance, edit server properties, manage worlds and backups, and install compatible mods from Modrinth.</p>
  </description>
